<plot>Joined Together? is an intimate portrait of four interfaith couples exploring the challenges of a Jewish - non-Jewish marriage. As these intermarried couples search for some common ground in faith and tradition, they discover a spiritual basis for an enduring unity with each other and come to some unexpected conclusions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?278884</url></doc>
